    <item>
      <title>日本央行明确加息指引安抚市场但可能适得其反</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/boj-s-clear-guidance-on-rate-hike-calms-markets-but-may-backfire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田和夫将利率提高至 2008 年以来的最高水平，通过谨慎地向投资者传达他的计划，避免了市场动荡。但这一策略本身也存在风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/boj-s-clear-guidance-on-rate-hike-calms-markets-but-may-backfire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 13:30:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>先锋集团标普 500 指数基金即将成为全球最大 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/vanguard-s-s-p-500-fund-about-to-overtake-state-street-s-become-world-s-top-etf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[似乎势不可挡的资金洪流使得先锋集团 (Vanguard Group Inc.) 即将夺走道富银行 (State Street Corp.) 数十年来一直占据的王冠。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/vanguard-s-s-p-500-fund-about-to-overtake-state-street-s-become-world-s-top-etf</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 13:29:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队就银行监管机构人选展开辩论，乔普拉仍留在消费者金融保护局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-team-debates-bank-watchdog-picks-as-chopra-remains-at-cfpb</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着拜登时代任命的两位银行监管机构负责人本周继续上班，一些唐纳德·特朗普的支持者开始质疑，为什么总统没有提名人来领导这些机构，或者至少解雇现任负责人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-team-debates-bank-watchdog-picks-as-chopra-remains-at-cfpb</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 13:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普推动欧佩克增产 雪佛龙哈萨克斯坦油田扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/chevron-s-kazakhstan-oil-field-expands-as-trump-pushes-opec</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司周五宣布，其对哈萨克斯坦田吉兹油田的扩建工程已完成，预计到今年年中，该油田的日产量将达到 100 万桶。]]></description>
